article_title: AG: Last 2 behavioral health providers cleared of Medicaid fraud
article_text:
Taos, NM (87571)

Today

Partly cloudy.

Tonight

Partly to mostly cloudy. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low near 35F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph.

article_metadata.author:
Justin Horwath and Steve Terrell
The New Mexican

og.description: The New Mexico Attorney General’s Office on Tuesday (April 5) ended a nearly three-year investigation into publicly funded behavioral health care, saying it failed to find evidence of criminal activity
